data.description: ONE-OF-A-KIND! Custom-built home on a large 31,250 sqft lot. Built in 2010. 4bd/3bth plus office or bonus room for a total 2493 sqft. Perfect for 2 working professionals from home or a big family.   Good size bedrooms; 2 are en suite. Rooms are large. Below the house, there is a concrete slab (3,014 sqft) with covered parking or patio, and a nice large bar that can seat 15 people for entertaining. 20 KW propane generator. Large kitchen with custom concrete counter tops, custom edges, and inlays. Doorways have nice bamboo trim. Walk in pantry. 2 on-demand water heaters. Jetted tubs in two of the bathrooms. Commercial grade bamboo flooring. Surround sound system, Impact windows & doors. Back and front patio decks. Metal roof.  Paver driveway.  Plenty of room for a pool, vehicles, and boat. Three entrances to the five lots for additions or parking. 2 other large concrete slabs on property.  County owned property across whole street. Only 4 owners on side of street; this is on all having multiple lots. Beach within 10 mins, public boat ramps, and parks.
